---
const baseUrl = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="relative mt-32 overflow-hidden border-t border-neutral-200/50 dark:border-white/5">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-accent/[0.02] to-accent/[0.04] dark:via-accent/[0.03] dark:to-accent/[0.06]"></div>
  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-16">
    <div class="grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-[1.5fr_1fr_1fr_1fr]">
      <div class="space-y-5">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <img src={baseUrl + 'assets/logo.png'} width={40} height={40} alt="Fun Phone" class="rounded-xl" loading="lazy" />
          <div>
            <p class="font-display text-lg font-extrabold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">Fun Phone</p>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent">Dialer & Contacts</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="max-w-xs text-sm leading-relaxed text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400" x-show="lang==='es'">
          Tu central inteligente de comunicaciones y productividad. Sin anuncios. Sin datos compartidos. Solo herramientas que funcionan.
        </p>
        <p class="max-w-xs text-sm leading-relaxed text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400" x-show="lang==='en'">
          Your smart hub for communication and productivity. No ads. No data sharing. Just tools that work.
        </p>
        <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bookverse.contacts" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-accent px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-lg shadow-accent/20 transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-accent/30">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 20.5v-17c0-.8.9-1.3 1.6-.8l14.4 8.5c.7.4.7 1.2 0 1.6L4.6 21.3c-.7.5-1.6 0-1.6-.8z"/></svg>
          Google Play
        </a>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500">
          <span x-show="lang==='es'">Producto</span>
          <span x-show="lang==='en'">Product</span>
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li><a href={baseUrl + 'features/'} class="text-neutral-600 transition hover:text-accent dark:text-neutral-400 dark:hover:text-accent"><span x-show="lang==='es'">Funciones</span><span x-show="lang==='en'">Features</span></a></li>
          <li><a href={baseUrl + 'roadmap/'} class="text-neutral-600 transition hover:text-accent dark:text-neutral-400 dark:hover:text-accent">Roadmap</a></li>
          <li><a href={baseUrl + 'faq/'} class="text-neutral-600 transition hover:text-accent dark:text-neutral-400 dark:hover:text-accent">FAQ</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500">
          <span x-show="lang==='es'">Legal</span>
          <span x-show="lang==='en'">Legal</span>
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li><a href={baseUrl + 'privacy/'} class="text-neutral-600 transition hover:text-accent dark:text-neutral-400 dark:hover:text-accent"><span x-show="lang==='es'">Privacidad</span><span x-show="lang==='en'">Privacy</span></a></li>
          <li><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bookverse.contacts&hl=es&gl=US" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-neutral-600 transition hover:text-accent dark:text-neutral-400 dark:hover:text-accent">Google Play</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500">
          <span x-show="lang==='es'">Soporte</span>
          <span x-show="lang==='en'">Support</span>
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li><a href="mailto:santiago.moncada.dev@gmail.com" class="text-neutral-600 transition hover:text-accent dark:text-neutral-400 dark:hover:text-accent"><span x-show="lang==='es'">Contacto</span><span x-show="lang==='en'">Contact</span></a></li>
          <li><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bookverse.contacts&hl=es&gl=US" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-neutral-600 transition hover:text-accent dark:text-neutral-400 dark:hover:text-accent"><span x-show="lang==='es'">Calificar</span><span x-show="lang==='en'">Rate us</span></a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-14 flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-4 border-t border-neutral-200/50 pt-8 text-xs text-neutral-400 dark:border-white/5 dark:text-neutral-500 sm:flex-row">
      <p>&copy; {year} Fun Phone &middot; Bookverse</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
        <span class="inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shadow-sm shadow-emerald-500/50"></span>
        <span x-show="lang==='es'">Datos 100% locales &middot; Sin anuncios</span>
        <span x-show="lang==='en'">100% local data &middot; Ad-free</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
